 />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月亮臉有福架喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係反月亮臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c9a55705c8e522f58202cf8df13bd78a91bb41","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原本係歪到一定要做？定係少少瑕疵，想變靚d?</blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月亮臉有福架喎</blockquote><br />\n突到成個猩猩 原始人咁既樣... 無福可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e34d0fb7753d4f2568d8af897ae0cdd24e4e2e1","tid":460111,"uid":74933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"點解唔係香港做？"},{"pid":"16c2cc6f86497c6fe67452904b98b83dc42c8c1a","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔係香港做？</blockquote><br />\n公立排到2046, 私家太貴<br />\n台灣好似出名d"},{"pid":"9e78efef3822f057364fb4840afb6fd58688318d","tid":460111,"uid":65629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d6bd7833929ceeb49969812600aca027b94a2c","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我其實都係第一次全身麻醉,成世仔未入過醫院"},{"pid":"c3644fc9dfc99b4891608bc1a700019119beb982","tid":460111,"uid":22558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"全身麻醉一訓醒就響病房 無野的"},{"pid":"484c6c14ab17f28e63622d453686768017e4231d","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全身麻醉一訓醒就響病房 無野的</bloc