0Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>全身麻醉一訓醒就響病房 無野的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過兩日答你<br />\n但我上網見d 人做完好少提個痛字"},{"pid":"ce8e6c4c17ca28b867a76a1e026feae2b804f13d","tid":460111,"uid":71220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全身麻醉一訓醒就響病房 無野的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過兩日答你<br />\n但我上網見d 人做完好少提個痛字</blockquote><br />\n巴打睇邊個醫生？ 我都plan緊去台灣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa97cd039f9180c95b2f479ed541c09712bd3fe2","tid":460111,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c2e7e1d7548859522370e5df79d9b12190b9e00","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全身麻醉一訓醒就響病房 無野的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過兩日答你<br />\n但我上網見d 人做完好少提個痛字</blockquote><br />\n巴打睇邊個醫生？ 我都plan緊去台灣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n謝x吉"},{"pid":"d3f1eb5dad404d606adde72fe9a1ecf7319aaa8b","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a639244ad78391cb5543fed4aaaaeee235abac1","tid":460111,"uid":71220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:16:20.00