我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n箍完... 但箍前箍後外觀無分別<br />\n本身牙都齊"},{"pid":"b62739464c1307a2625de2d9a2c7139b754cf133","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原本係歪到一定要做？定係少少瑕疵，想變靚d?</blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n同埋你係上下做晒？</blockquote><br />\n係呀... 醫生解釋我下顎異常生長...變成戽斗...上顎因為要追住下顎順遁出埋黎秉以變左嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4781af09378dd78fd5cccfee687722989c941afa","tid":460111,"uid":63657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T16:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原本係歪到一定要做？定係少少瑕疵，想變靚d?</blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n我都係倒及牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但去台灣做人生路不熟<br />\n應該由邊到埋手好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接去台灣搵專科定要預約<br />\n覆診時台港兩地走次數密唔密<br />\n好多疑問求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97e40d559bc6b380f47fdc9a8fd36e6ac4f0cf5","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原本係歪到一定要做？定係少少瑕疵，想變靚d?</blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n我都係倒及牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但去台灣做人生路不熟<br />\n應該由邊到埋手好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接去台灣搵專科定要預約<br />\n覆診時台港兩地走次數密唔密<br />\n好多疑問求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係去台灣 整型診所,要事前預約先<br />\n其實係手術後覆診一次（7日後）"},{"pid":"5e2434c9cffc7abb2dab8cb68e61e8b58720094e","tid":460111,"uid":130586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:30:08.000Z","msg":"一年前做左<br />\n痛就唔多痛<br />\n係好脹痛唔舒服咁<br />\n同埋果時全身麻醉 做完個人又無力 面又脹到痴左線<br />\n用左成個月體力先恢復<br />\n<br />\n樓主係術後鎖口果隻定打金屬片落顎骨？"},{"pid":"7197a90cc1f06d49602941fd462ca0ab506aabf6","tid":460111,"uid":64282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原本係歪到一定要做？定係少少瑕疵，想變靚d?</blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n同埋你係上下做晒？</blockquote><br />\n係呀... 醫生解釋我下顎異常生長...變成戽斗...上顎因為要追住下顎順遁出埋黎秉以變左嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係咬合正常<br />\n巴打幾歲"},{"pid":"5dcd3ae2f303cca1cd938