ji\" />"},{"pid":"49f920b0ca288682ef57d7acd1a87f817710b6e3","tid":460111,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人都要整容"},{"pid":"bf2b237427c72a993a08a579d7017c6ca1d69663","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n同埋你係上下做晒？</blockquote><br />\n係呀... 醫生解釋我下顎異常生長...變成戽斗...上顎因為要追住下顎順遁出埋黎秉以變左嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係咬合正常<br />\n巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n24呀... 巴打你會唔會做正顎<br />\n我係番工先蓄到手術錢. 無問屋企人拎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n24草到手術錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我24先得幾皮野😞</blockquote><br />\n今日打開e,banking 望... 黎緊日日食面包lu"},{"pid":"4601c35c450634e0288ef52d38b56b09ce5f2ddb","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原本係歪到一定要做？定係少少瑕疵，想變靚d?</blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n我都係倒及牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但去台灣做人生路不熟<br />\n應該由邊到埋手好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直接去台灣搵專科定要預約<br />\n覆診時台港兩地走次數密唔密<br />\n好多疑問求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係去台灣 整型診所,要事前預約先<br />\n其實係手術後覆診一次（7日後）</blockquote><br />\n有冇診所資料可以share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔識講國語可唔可以用wtsapp溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醫師叫 謝明吉,佢地用line"},{"pid":"0ee2e827937419dd3af2c3bde67ac4e989e613a2","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係成功既例子<br />\n6年前做左手術 上下顎都要打爆晒重組<br />\n開頭果一兩年比較面腫 尤其個鼻<br />\n之後已經靚仔晒 但係手術開刀果個牙位要注意<br />\n一定要勤戴固定器 如果唔係郁位極快</blockquote><br />\n捱過就得了"},{"pid":"1f53d6b00499e02651c55a42d56ed90811c07a0c","tid":460111,"uid":64282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原本係歪到一定要做？定係少少瑕疵，想變靚d?</blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n同埋你係上下做晒？</blockquote><br />\n係呀... 醫生解釋我下顎異常生長...變成戽斗...上顎因為要追住下顎順遁出埋黎秉以變左嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係咬合正常<br />\n巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n24呀... 巴打你會唔會做正顎<br />\n我係番工先蓄到手術錢. 無問屋企人拎</blockquote><br />\n一直都好想<br />\n但我出年先畢業<br />\n可能要儲兩年錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十萬係只係手術費？"},{"pid":"cb3741fef95e41c561090a6c25a37ef49e7313f5","tid":460111,"uid":64282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下星期香港做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你驚唔驚, 你手術費用幾多？</blockquote><br />\n排菲臘牙科，cool完幾個月有得做，唔洗錢，係出反自己啲住院同物料費</blockquote><br />\n菲臘已經唔收手術case了"},{"pid":"3db8b250ab51ca7d26d26be0cd3cc184a2fad4ad","tid":460111,"uid":114774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"祝好運<br />\n利申睇過點做"},{"pid":"10d2fc58236266d94422e4ac44efd4570eb4089c","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T11:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我係月亮臉 + 嘴突, 咬合正常<br />\n講到尾想側面好睇D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n同埋你係上下做晒？</blockquote><br />\n係呀... 醫生解釋我下顎異常生長...變成戽斗...上顎因為要追住下顎順遁出埋黎秉以變左嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係咬合正常<br />\n巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n24呀... 巴打你會唔會做正顎<br />\n我係番工先蓄到手術錢. 無問屋企人拎</blockquote><br />\n一直都好想<br />\n但我出年先畢業<br />\n可能要儲兩年錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十萬係只係手術費？</blockquote><br />\n36 萬台幣係手術費<br />\n實際資詢同做手術來回台灣兩次再加係到既住宿, 我做完手術都係住青年旅舍慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ab0c26dbe895134ef0c61cde5c9ba7b629beff","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祝好運<br />\n利申睇過點做</blockquote><br />\n唉... 過多十幾句鐘就係手術床. 唔諗咁多"},{"pid":"b6aead76675ec8431d7ee0a8ee45638a8058d7d9","tid":460111,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>祝好運<br />\n利申睇過點做</blockquote><br />\n唉... 過多十幾句鐘就係手術床. 唔諗咁多</blockquote><br />\nZZZ起物先算啦"},{"pid":"8008b1cabe6d62249a27b4dc3ea63bc9f0ed5ea1","tid":460111,"uid":64282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望兩年後做<br />\ncool左牙未？</blockquote><br />\n同埋你係上下做晒？</blockquote><br />\n係呀... 醫生解釋我下顎異常生長...變成戽斗...上顎因為要追住下顎順遁出埋黎秉以變左嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係咬合正常<br />\n巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n24呀... 巴打你會唔會做正顎<br />\n我係番工先蓄到手術錢. 無問屋企人拎</blockquote><br />\n一直都好想<br />\n但我出年先畢業<br />\n可能要儲兩年錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十萬係只係手術費？</blockquote><br />\n36 萬台幣係手術費<br />\n實際資詢同做手術來回台灣兩次再加係到既住宿, 我做完手術都係住青年旅舍慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手術完洗唔洗鎖口<br />\n唔洗既話好好多"},{"pid":"8ca9011fe8fcd947c1218bd2dcc69351e57bd514","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n同埋你係上下做晒？</blockquote><br />\n係呀... 醫生解釋我下顎異常生長...變成戽斗...上顎因為要追住下顎順遁出埋黎秉以變左嘴突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同我一樣<img src=