來回台灣兩次再加係到既住宿, 我做完手術都係住青年旅舍慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手術完洗唔洗鎖口<br />\n唔洗既話好好多</blockquote><br />\n原來要鎖口7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7日都算快架啦<br />\n做完會係台灣留幾耐先番香港？"},{"pid":"1ceddebaa3a03be613d8d04bcec63d06b280126f","tid":460111,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:25:07.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"01b3d58a30507b14593b4e68bd3cd8e6e0dae8b3","tid":460111,"uid":9056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T13:35:48.000Z","msg":"一個月前做完 成個過程最痛係抆尿喉個下 真係成世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他無咩野<br />\n做之前食多d好野 買定罐加營素 同埋即沖薯蓉 放係屋企"},{"pid":"8cc643ab1d27461dfbdedad5a2043f1db929228e","tid":460111,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算唔算整容？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得算</blockquote><br />\n名正言順既整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b5a4188b6c7c38050ac0da88c304cd78ed7561","tid":460111,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"472ef5a5cdd38c843be7cf3a780f70053d0c66cd","tid":460111,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"台灣做都要十萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b61de2cf686cec53933f1255a1a7096c91fe87","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月前做完 成個過程最痛係抆尿喉個下 真係成世都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他無咩野<br />\n做之前食多d好野 買定罐加營素 同埋即沖薯蓉 放係屋企</blockquote><br />\n頂...我最驚拔尿喉...你講完我即刻唔想做"},{"pid":"b2985afcd8fd0ed466a31fa0cae9c0c0f586efcb","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係咬合正常<br />\n巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n24呀... 巴打你會唔會做正顎<br />\n我係番工先蓄到手術錢. 無問屋企人拎</blockquote><br />\n一直都好想<br />\n但我出年先畢業<br />\n可能要儲兩年錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十萬係只係手術費？</blockquote><br />\n36 萬台幣係手術費<br />\n實際資詢同做手術來回台灣兩次再加係到既住宿, 我做完手術都係住青年旅舍慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手術完洗唔洗鎖口<br />\n唔洗既話好好多</blockquote><br />\n原來要鎖口7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7日都算快架啦<br />\n做完會係台灣留幾耐先番香港？</blockquote><br />\n由手術當日計會留10日"},{"pid":"61220eeba1d756dd54b4a882603963a1df4d8a8a","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間</blockquote><br />\n謝&times;吉 (風華）<br />\ngoogle 實有"},{"pid":"acc368db7e33ed92d1743568752818a3199fd430","tid":460111,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"我都係突嘴，想做但又驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名等報告"},{"pid":"b55403d61bc05e6954c9f1459d6aa161a7bbdb7d","tid":460111,"uid":67634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"今日見最後一次醫生. 呢個醫生係勁有自信果種人...我同佢講香港做下顎都要3~4句鐘,佢同我做上下顎用4個鐘內<br />\n<br />\n佢9成病人第二日出院. 出血量220cc內， 聲稱少過捐血,叫我唔好拎香港醫生同佢比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢另外提個重點係香港醫生唔多理外觀"},{"pid":"4754dde